Use Case: Roll Dice

Actors: Fortnite Monopoly User

Description: Once it's the Player's turn, they are prompted to roll the dice.
The game randomly generates two numbers, 1 through 6, that are added together.
The Player moves the randomly generated number of spaces.
If the two dice roll the same number, they Player gets to roll again.
On completion, the Player's turn ends and cannot move until their next turn.

Cross Ref.: Must be the beginning of the player's turn, or must have previously rolled doubles.

Use-Cases: Previous Player must have selected next turn, completing their turn.
